ChangeLog
===================================================

2026-05-13 (2.1.2)
    1. Add Rules Mode (Whitelist / Blacklist). In Blacklist mode the rules list
       becomes a proxy list — only matching domains/IPs go through the proxy,
       everything else goes DIRECT. Implemented via a synthesized PAC script
       since chrome.proxy.settings has no native blacklist.
    2. Store the blacklist (proxy list) independently of the whitelist (bypass
       list); each list keeps its own content when switching modes.
    3. China List now applies to Whitelist mode only.
    4. Add Help -> Changelog panel.

2026-05-13 (2.1.1)
    1. Move proxy-type switching from options into the popup.
    2. Refresh popup/options UI: teal accent, dark mode, mode-icon tiles.
    3. Polish options page: stronger Profiles bar, subtler sidebar mark.
    4. Tone down popup header logo.
    5. Fix bypass-list hint icon wrapping to its own line.
    6. Translate profile-bar strings to ja and ru.

2026-05-08 (2.1.0)
    1. Add multi-profile support: each profile holds a complete proxy
       configuration; switch the active profile from the popup or via Alt+P.
    2. Add Help -> Usage section in options page.
    3. Translate the Usage section to ja and ru.

2026-03-12 (2.0.4)
    1. Drop QUIC proxy support (Chrome no longer exposes it to extensions).

2026-03-11 (2.0.3)
    1. Further extension UI enhancements.
    2. Add missing ja translations.

2026-03-09 (2.0.2)
    1. Multiple popup UI enhancements.
    2. Better bypass-list hint message.
    3. Add missing i18n strings.

2025-12-31 (2.0.1)
    1. Add Go proxy quick-link to the options menu.
    2. Add example.pac and PAC-script proxy details in README / FAQ.
    3. Refresh ru and ja translations.
    4. Improve hr style.

2024-08-26 (2.0.0)
    1. Migrate the extension from Manifest V2 to Manifest V3.
    2. Add automatic persistent-data migration when upgrading from MV2.
    3. Bump minimum Chrome version to 88 (required for MV3).

2022-1-5   (1.4.1)
    1. Updated Russian translation

2021-12-09 (1.3.9)
    1. fix popup.html

2021-12-07 (1.3.8)
    1. fix whitelist

2021-11-30 (1.3.7)
    1. UI improvement

2021-11-27 (1.3.6)
    1. add pac url support

2021-07-27
    1. use pac data instead of pac url
    2. update jquery to 3.6.0
    3. update Russian translation

2020-12-1 (1.3.3)
    1. bug fixed
    2. improve UI

2020-11-23 (1.3.0)
    1. support quic proxy
    2. delete file:// scheme in pac mode (chrome delete file:// support in extension)
    3. bugs fixed

